{"id":252568,"type":6,"name":"The Hitchhiker's Guide to the Galaxy","name_cn":"银河系漫游指南","date":"2005-04-28","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/24/3b/252568_JmNt7.jpg","rating":{"rank":1658,"total":22,"count":{"1":1,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":1,"6":3,"7":12,"8":4,"9":1,"10":0},"score":6.8},"summary":"阿瑟·登特自认为是个倒霉的地球人，生活中事事不顺，\r\n\r\n 他得知外星人为了一项银河高速公路的工程计划，而要除掉阻挡工程进行的障碍物——地球。他的好友福特·普里弗克特承认自己是个外星人，正在地球上寻找新版的《银河系漫游指南》。在福特的帮助下，在地球被毁灭前的最后一刻，阿瑟尔·登特搭上了一艘路过地球的外星人的太空船，远离这个即将毁灭的伤心地，开始了一段充满惊奇的星河冒险之旅。旅程中，阿瑟尔发现毛巾是宇宙间最有用的东西，并体验到了生命的全新意义，更发现所有他需要知道的一切居然都写在一本名叫《银河漫游指南》的电子图书里。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>银河系漫游指南</li><li><span>主演: </span><a href=\"/person/40610\">Martin Freeman</a>、<a href=\"/person/43866\">Helen Mirren</a>、<a href=\"/person/33472\">Stephen Fry</a>、<a href=\"/person/44799\">John Malkovich</a>、<a href=\"/person/40305\">Warwick Davis</a>、<a href=\"/person/40304\">Richard Griffiths</a>、<a href=\"/person/39647\">Alan Rickman</a>、<a href=\"/person/56766\">Sam Rockwell</a></li><li><span>集数: </span>1</li><li><span>开始: </span>2005年4月28日（英国）</li><li><span>类型: </span>科幻 / 冒险 / 喜剧</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>美国，英国</li><li><span>语言: </span>英语</li><li><span>每集长: </span>109分钟</li><li><span>imdb_id: </span>tt0371724</li>","collection":{"on_hold":0,"dropped":0,"wish":10,"collect":30,"doing":0},"tags":[{"name":"电影","count":10},{"name":"科幻","count":8},{"name":"喜剧","count":7},{"name":"欧美","count":4},{"name":"英国","count":3},{"name":"2005","count":3},{"name":"太空歌剧","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":806138,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/806138","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":""}],"staff":[{"id":56766,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/79/35/56766_prsn_IiwV3.jpg","name":"Sam Rockwell","desc":"主演"},{"id":40304,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/b1/57/40304_prsn_TnGZ9.jpg","name":"Richard Griffiths","desc":"主演"},{"id":39647,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/de/54/39647_prsn_CmsZ7.jpg","name":"Alan Rickman","desc":"主演"},{"id":40305,"image":"//lain.bg